            "id": 6416977,
            "title": "盤中速報 - Crowdstrike控股(CRWD-US)大跌5.06%，報374.7美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Crowdstrike控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRWD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRWD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRWD-US</a>)截至台北時間10日21:50股價下跌19.99美元，報374.70美元，跌幅5.06%，成交量1,154,949（股），盤中最高價398.05美元、最低價374.51美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.51%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.07%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.43%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+2.46%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Crowdstrike控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRWD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRWD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRWD-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-1.11%</li> <li>近 1 月：-9.09%</li> <li>近 3 月：-16.13%</li> <li>近 6 月：-22.48%</li> <li>今年以來：-15.8%</li></ul></section></main>",
